  <body dur="03:47.150">
    <div begin="00:09.990" end="03:47.150">
      <p begin="00:09.990" end="00:10.170" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L1"><span begin="00:09.990" end="00:10.170">Uh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">嗯</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">嗯</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">ああ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ay</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">É</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ох</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ah</span></p>
      <p begin="00:11.690" end="00:14.060" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L2"><span begin="00:11.690" end="00:11.860">If</span> <span begin="00:11.860" end="00:12.020">they</span> <span begin="00:12.020" end="00:12.240">saw</span> <span begin="00:12.240" end="00:12.410">wha</span><span begin="00:12.410" end="00:12.450">t</span> <span begin="00:12.450" end="00:12.920">I</span> <span begin="00:13.020" end="00:14.060">saw</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">倘若他们能看见我眼中的风景</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">倘若他們能看見我眼中的風景</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">僕が見たものを彼らが見たなら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내가 본 걸 그들도 보았다면</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">S'ils voyaient ce que j'ai vu</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Si vieran lo que yo vi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn sie sähen was ich sah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Se eles vissem o que eu vi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Если бы они видели то что видел я</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Se vedessero quello che ho visto io</span></p>
      <p begin="00:14.780" end="00:16.940" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="00:14.780" end="00:14.930">They</span> <span begin="00:14.930" end="00:15.090">would</span> <span begin="00:15.090" end="00:15.460">fall</span> <span begin="00:15.460" end="00:15.830">the</span> <span begin="00:15.830" end="00:16.170">way</span> <span begin="00:16.170" end="00:16.300">I</span> <span begin="00:16.430" end="00:16.940">fell</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">他们定会像我这般无可救药地沦陷</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">他們定會像我這般無可救藥地淪陷</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">僕のように恋に落ちるだろう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나처럼 너에게 빠졌을 텐데</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ils tomberaient comme je suis tombé</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Se enamorarían como yo me enamoré</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Würden sie sich verlieben wie ich mich verliebte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eles se apaixonariam do jeito que me apaixonei</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Они бы влюбились так же как влюбился я</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Perderebbero la testa come l'ho persa io</span></p>
      <p begin="00:16.980" end="00:19.390" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:16.980" end="00:17.050">But</span> <span begin="00:17.160" end="00:17.320">they</span> <span begin="00:17.320" end="00:17.510">don't</span> <span begin="00:17.510" end="00:17.660">know</span> <span begin="00:17.660" end="00:17.850">what</span> <span begin="00:17.850" end="00:18.500">you</span> <span begin="00:18.500" end="00:19.330">wan</span><span begin="00:19.330" end="00:19.390">t</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">但他们不懂你心底的渴望</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">但他們不懂你心底的渴望</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">でも君が何を望んでいるか 彼らは知らない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">하지만 그들은 네가 뭘 원하는지 몰라</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Mais ils ne savent pas ce que tu veux</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Pero ellos no saben lo que tú quieres</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Aber sie wissen nicht was du willst</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mas eles não sabem o que você quer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Но они не знают чего ты хочешь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ma loro non sanno cosa desideri</span></p>
      <p begin="00:20.050" end="00:22.480" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:20.050" end="00:20.220">And,</span> <span begin="00:20.220" end="00:20.400">ba</span><span begin="00:20.400" end="00:20.600">by,</span> <span begin="00:20.600" end="00:20.920">I</span> <span begin="00:20.920" end="00:21.100">woul</span><span begin="00:21.100" end="00:21.260">d</span> <span begin="00:21.260" end="00:21.600">ne</span><span begin="00:21.600" end="00:21.940">ver</span> <span begin="00:21.940" end="00:22.480">tell</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">而宝贝 我也绝不会向外人言说</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">而寶貝 我也絕不會向外人言說</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">そしてベイビー 僕が教えることは絶対にない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그리고, 베이비, 난 절대 말해주지 않을 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Et bébé je ne le dirais jamais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Y, nena, yo nunca se los diría</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Und Schatz ich würde es niemals verraten</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">E, baby, eu nunca contaria</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">И малышка я им ни за что не расскажу</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">E, piccola, io non lo direi mai</span></p>
      <p begin="00:22.620" end="00:24.900" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:22.620" end="00:22.690">I</span><span begin="00:22.690" end="00:22.780">f</span> <span begin="00:22.780" end="00:22.970">they</span> <span begin="00:22.970" end="00:23.120">knew</span> <span begin="00:23.120" end="00:23.310">wha</span><span begin="00:23.310" end="00:23.340">t</span> <span begin="00:23.340" end="00:24.010">I</span> <span begin="00:24.010" end="00:24.900">know</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">倘若他们知晓我拥有的秘密</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">倘若他們知曉我擁有的秘密</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">僕が知っていることを彼らが知ったなら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내가 아는 걸 그들도 알았다면</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">S'ils savaient ce que je sais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Si supieran lo que yo sé</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn sie wüssten was ich weiß</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Se eles soubessem o que eu sei</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Если бы они знали то что знаю я</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Se sapessero quello che so</span></p>
      <p begin="00:25.670" end="00:27.990" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:25.670" end="00:25.860">They</span> <span begin="00:25.860" end="00:25.940">would</span> <span begin="00:26.060" end="00:26.370">ne</span><span begin="00:26.370" end="00:26.750">ver</span> <span begin="00:26.750" end="00:27.070">let</span> <span begin="00:27.070" end="00:27.400">you</span> <span begin="00:27.400" end="00:27.990">go</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">他们绝对舍不得放开你的手</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">他們絕對捨不得放開你的手</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">決して君を手放さないだろう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">절대 널 놓아주지 않았을 텐데</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ils ne te laisseraient jamais partir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Nunca te dejarían ir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Würden sie dich niemals gehen lassen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eles nunca te deixariam ir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Они бы никогда тебя не отпустили</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non ti lascerebbero mai andare</span></p>
      <p begin="00:28.230" end="00:29.410" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:28.230" end="00:28.410">So</span> <span begin="00:28.410" end="00:28.660">gue</span><span begin="00:28.660" end="00:28.790">ss</span> <span begin="00:28.790" end="00:29.410">what?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">所以你知道吗？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">所以你知道嗎？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">だからどうだか分かるかい</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그래서 그거 알아?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Alors devine quoi ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Así que ¿adivina qué?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Also weißt du was</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Então adivinha?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Так что знаешь что</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Quindi indovina un po'?</span></p>
      <p begin="00:29.770" end="00:32.060" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:29.770" end="00:29.940">I</span> <span begin="00:29.940" end="00:30.130">ain't</span> <span begin="00:30.130" end="00:30.480">ne</span><span begin="00:30.480" end="00:30.830">ver</span> <span begin="00:30.830" end="00:31.020">let</span><span begin="00:31.020" end="00:31.170">ting</span> <span begin="00:31.170" end="00:31.380">you</span> <span begin="00:31.480" end="00:32.060">go</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我生生世世都不会放你离开</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我生生世世都不會放你離開</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">僕は絶対に君を手放さない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">난 절대 널 놓지 않을 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne te laisserai jamais partir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Yo nunca te dejaré ir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich werde dich niemals gehen lassen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu nunca vou te deixar ir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я тебя никогда не отпущу</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Io non ti lascerò mai andare</span></p>
      <p begin="00:32.130" end="00:35.060" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="00:32.130" end="00:32.800">'Cau</span><span begin="00:32.800" end="00:32.860">se</span> <span begin="00:32.860" end="00:33.390">your</span> <span begin="00:33.390" end="00:33.540">li</span><span begin="00:33.540" end="00:33.740">ps</span> <span begin="00:33.740" end="00:33.920">were</span> <span begin="00:34.050" end="00:34.330">made</span> <span begin="00:34.330" end="00:34.440">for</span> <span begin="00:34.560" end="00:35.060">mine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">只因你的双唇天生就该被我亲吻</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">只因你的雙唇天生就該被我親吻</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君の唇は僕のものになるために作られたから</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">네 입술은 내 입술을 위해 만들어졌으니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Car tes lèvres ont été faites pour les miennes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Porque tus labios fueron hechos para los míos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Denn deine Lippen sind für meine gemacht</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Porque os seus lábios foram feitos para os meus</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ведь твои губы созданы для моих</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Perché le tue labbra sono state fatte per le mie</span></p>
      <p begin="00:35.400" end="00:37.710" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="00:35.400" end="00:35.580">And</span> <span begin="00:35.580" end="00:36.060">my</span> <span begin="00:36.060" end="00:36.270">heart</span> <span begin="00:36.400" end="00:36.470">would</span> <span begin="00:36.590" end="00:36.750">go</span> <span begin="00:36.850" end="00:36.950">f</span><span begin="00:36.950" end="00:37.280">lat</span><span begin="00:37.280" end="00:37.710">line</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我的心跳大概会骤然停息</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我的心跳大概會驟然停息</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">そして僕の心臓は止まってしまうだろう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내 심장은 멈춰버리고 말 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Et mon cœur s'arrêterait de battre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Y mi corazón se detendría</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Und mein Herz würde aufhören zu schlagen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">E o meu coração iria parar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">А моё сердце бы просто остановилось</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">E il mio battito si azzererebbe</span></p>
      <p begin="00:38.110" end="00:41.990" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="00:38.110" end="00:38.200">I</span><span begin="00:38.200" end="00:38.300">f</span> <span begin="00:38.300" end="00:38.680">i</span><span begin="00:38.680" end="00:38.750">t</span> <span begin="00:38.750" end="00:39.020">wa</span><span begin="00:39.020" end="00:39.150">s</span><span begin="00:39.150" end="00:39.340">n't</span> <span begin="00:39.480" end="00:39.840">bea</span><span begin="00:39.840" end="00:39.980">ting</span> <span begin="00:39.980" end="00:40.380">for</span> <span begin="00:40.380" end="00:40.570">you</span> <span begin="00:40.680" end="00:41.020">all</span> <span begin="00:41.020" end="00:41.070">the</span> <span begin="00:41.190" end="00:41.990">time</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">倘若它不是每时每刻都在为你跳动</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">倘若它不是每時每刻都在為你跳動</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">いつも君のために脈打っていなければ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">항상 널 위해 뛰고 있는 게 아니라면</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">S'il ne battait pas pour toi tout le temps</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Si no estuviera latiendo por ti todo el tiempo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn es nicht die ganze Zeit nur für dich schlagen würde</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Se não estivesse batendo por você o tempo todo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Если бы оно не билось всё время ради тебя</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Se non battesse per te tutto il tempo</span></p>
      <p begin="00:42.480" end="00:46.990" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="00:42.480" end="00:42.740">So</span> <span begin="00:42.740" end="00:42.830">i</span><span begin="00:42.830" end="00:42.910">f</span> <span begin="00:42.910" end="00:43.260">I</span> <span begin="00:43.260" end="00:43.630">get</span> <span begin="00:43.730" end="00:44.130">jea</span><span begin="00:44.130" end="00:44.250">lou</span><span begin="00:44.250" end="00:44.420">s,</span> <span begin="00:45.630" end="00:45.950">I</span> <span begin="00:45.950" end="00:46.410">can</span><span begin="00:46.410" end="00:46.480">'t</span> <span begin="00:46.480" end="00:46.840">hel</span><span begin="00:46.840" end="00:46.880">p</span> <span begin="00:46.880" end="00:46.990">it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">所以若我吃醋嫉妒 那也是情难自禁</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">所以若我吃醋嫉妒 那也是情難自禁</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">だから嫉妬しても 仕方がないんだ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그러니 내가 질투하더라도, 어쩔 수 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Alors si je suis jaloux je n'y peux rien</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Así que si me pongo celoso, no puedo evitarlo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn ich also eifersüchtig werde kann ich nichts dafür</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Então se eu fico com ciúmes, não consigo evitar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Поэтому если я ревную ничего не могу с собой поделать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Quindi se divento geloso, non ci posso fare niente</span></p>
