      <p begin="02:19.160" end="02:21.180" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L42"><span begin="02:19.160" end="02:19.370">You</span> <span begin="02:19.370" end="02:19.460">mu</span><span begin="02:19.460" end="02:19.570">st</span> <span begin="02:19.570" end="02:19.770">be</span> <span begin="02:19.770" end="02:19.900">an</span> <span begin="02:19.900" end="02:20.230">an</span><span begin="02:20.230" end="02:21.180">gel</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你一定是不慎坠入凡间的天使</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你一定是不慎墜入凡間的天使</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君は天使に違いない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">넌 틀림없이 천사일 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tu dois être un ange</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Debes ser un ángel</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Du musst ein Engel sein</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Você deve ser um anjo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ты должно быть ангел</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Devi essere un angelo</span></p>
      <p begin="02:21.920" end="02:23.220" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L43"><span begin="02:21.920" end="02:22.040">Pu</span><span begin="02:22.040" end="02:22.120">t</span> <span begin="02:22.120" end="02:22.310">you</span> <span begin="02:22.310" end="02:22.450">in</span> <span begin="02:22.450" end="02:22.560">a</span> <span begin="02:22.560" end="02:22.630">f</span><span begin="02:22.630" end="02:22.970">rame,</span> <span begin="02:22.970" end="02:23.220">ooh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">真想把你珍藏进画框里 喔</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">真想把你珍藏進畫框裡 喔</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君を額縁に飾りたい</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">널 액자에 담아두고 싶어, 우</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Te mettre dans un cadre ouh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Te pondría en un marco, oh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich würde dich am liebsten einrahmen oh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Te colocaria numa moldura, ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Поместить бы тебя в рамку оох</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Da metterti in una cornice, oh</span></p>
      <p begin="02:23.290" end="02:24.570" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L44"><span begin="02:23.290" end="02:23.460">Ba</span><span begin="02:23.460" end="02:23.630">by,</span> <span begin="02:23.630" end="02:23.800">who</span> <span begin="02:23.800" end="02:23.970">could</span> <span begin="02:23.970" end="02:24.010">b</span><span begin="02:24.010" end="02:24.330">lame</span> <span begin="02:24.330" end="02:24.570">you?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">宝贝 谁又能舍得怪你呢？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">寶貝 誰又能捨得怪你呢？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">ベイビー 誰が君を責められる</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">베이비, 누가 널 탓하겠어?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Bébé qui pourrait t'en blâmer ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Nena, ¿quién podría culparte?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Schatz wer könnte es dir verübeln</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Baby, quem poderia te culpar?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Малышка кто бы мог тебя винить</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Piccola, chi potrebbe biasimarti?</span></p>
      <p begin="02:24.640" end="02:26.320" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L45"><span begin="02:24.640" end="02:24.820">Gla</span><span begin="02:24.820" end="02:24.860">d</span> <span begin="02:24.860" end="02:25.020">your</span> <span begin="02:25.020" end="02:25.190">ma</span><span begin="02:25.190" end="02:25.360">ma</span> <span begin="02:25.360" end="02:25.670">ma</span><span begin="02:25.670" end="02:25.710">de</span> <span begin="02:25.710" end="02:26.320">you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">万分庆幸你母亲带你降临人世</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">萬分慶幸你母親帶你降臨人世</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君を産んでくれたママに感謝するよ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">널 낳아주신 네 어머니께 감사해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Heureux que ta maman t'ait faite</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Agradezco que tu mamá te haya dado la vida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Bin froh dass deine Mama dich zur Welt gebracht hat</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Que bom que a sua mãe te fez</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я так рад что твоя мама родила тебя</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sono grato che tua madre ti abbia messa al mondo</span></p>
      <p begin="02:27.390" end="02:28.660" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L46"><span begin="02:27.390" end="02:27.560">Ma</span><span begin="02:27.560" end="02:27.740">king</span> <span begin="02:27.740" end="02:27.880">me</span> <span begin="02:27.880" end="02:28.050">in</span><span begin="02:28.050" end="02:28.420">sane,</span> <span begin="02:28.420" end="02:28.660">you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">让我为你神魂颠倒的你</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">讓我為你神魂顛倒的你</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君は僕を夢中にさせる</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">날 미치게 만들어, 넌</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tu me rends fou</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Me vuelves loco, tú</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Du treibst mich in den Wahnsinn du</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Me deixando louco, você</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ты сводишь меня с ума</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Mi fai impazzire, tu</span></p>
