      <p begin="02:35.560" end="02:37.880" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L50"><span begin="02:35.560" end="02:35.940">Tat</span><span begin="02:36.060" end="02:36.410">too</span><span begin="02:36.410" end="02:36.460">ed</span> <span begin="02:36.460" end="02:36.950">your</span> <span begin="02:36.950" end="02:37.860">mar</span><span begin="02:37.860" end="02:37.880">k</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">将你的印记深深刻作刺青</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">將你的印記深深刻作刺青</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君の印を刻み込んだ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">네 흔적을 문신으로 새겼어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tu as tatoué ta marque</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Tatuaste tu marca</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Hast dein Zeichen tätowiert</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Tatuou a sua marca</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Оставила свой след словно тату</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Hai tatuato il tuo marchio</span></p>
      <p begin="02:38.300" end="02:42.350" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L51"><span begin="02:38.300" end="02:38.750">There</span> <span begin="02:38.750" end="02:39.180">for</span> <span begin="02:39.180" end="02:39.630">the</span> <span begin="02:39.630" end="02:40.170">whole</span> <span begin="02:40.170" end="02:40.430">world</span> <span begin="02:40.430" end="02:40.990">to</span> <span begin="02:40.990" end="02:42.350">see</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">就那样向全世界高调宣示</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">就那樣向全世界高調宣示</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">世界中に見えるように</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">온 세상이 다 볼 수 있도록</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Là pour que le monde entier la voie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ahí para que todo el mundo la vea</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dass die ganze Welt es sehen kann</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Lá para o mundo inteiro ver</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Чтобы видел весь мир</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Lì in modo che il mondo intero possa vederlo</span></p>
      <p begin="02:42.900" end="02:46.020" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L52"><span begin="02:42.900" end="02:43.220">You're</span> <span begin="02:43.220" end="02:43.650">the</span> <span begin="02:43.750" end="02:44.070">ow</span><span begin="02:44.070" end="02:44.240">ne</span><span begin="02:44.240" end="02:44.290">r</span> <span begin="02:44.290" end="02:44.520">o</span><span begin="02:44.520" end="02:44.620">f</span> <span begin="02:44.620" end="02:45.090">my</span> <span begin="02:45.090" end="02:45.980">hear</span><span begin="02:45.980" end="02:46.020">t</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你是我心房的唯一主人</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你是我心房的唯一主人</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君は僕の心の持ち主</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">넌 내 심장의 주인이야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tu es celle qui possède mon cœur</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Eres la dueña de mi corazón</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Du bist die Herrin meines Herzens</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Você é a dona do meu coração</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ты хозяйка моего сердца</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sei la padrona del mio cuore</span></p>
      <p begin="02:46.480" end="02:48.850" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L53"><span begin="02:46.480" end="02:46.860">An</span><span begin="02:46.980" end="02:47.010">d</span> <span begin="02:47.010" end="02:47.230">all</span> <span begin="02:47.350" end="02:47.650">my</span> <span begin="02:47.650" end="02:47.850">s</span><span begin="02:47.850" end="02:48.730">car</span><span begin="02:48.730" end="02:48.850">s</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">也抚平了我所有的伤痕</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">也撫平了我所有的傷痕</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">そして僕のすべての傷跡の</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내 모든 상처의 주인도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Et toutes mes cicatrices</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Y de todas mis cicatrices</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Und all meiner Narben</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">E de todas as minhas cicatrizes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">И всех моих шрамов</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">E di tutte le mie cicatrici</span></p>
      <p begin="02:49.200" end="02:53.310" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L54"><span begin="02:49.200" end="02:49.540">Ba</span><span begin="02:49.540" end="02:49.770">by,</span> <span begin="02:49.770" end="02:50.060">you</span> <span begin="02:50.060" end="02:50.500">got</span> <span begin="02:50.500" end="02:50.860">su</span><span begin="02:50.860" end="02:50.910">ch</span> <span begin="02:50.910" end="02:51.050">a</span> <span begin="02:51.050" end="02:51.420">hol</span><span begin="02:51.420" end="02:51.460">d</span> <span begin="02:51.460" end="02:51.770">on</span> <span begin="02:51.900" end="02:52.870">me,</span> <span begin="02:52.870" end="02:53.310">so</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">宝贝 你就是这样让我彻底沦陷 所以</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">寶貝 你就是這樣讓我徹底淪陷 所以</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">ベイビー 君は僕をすっかり夢中にさせているから</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">베이비, 넌 날 완전히 사로잡았어, 그러니</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Bébé tu as une telle emprise sur moi alors</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Nena, tienes tanto control sobre mí, así que</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Schatz du hast mich so sehr im Griff also</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Baby, você me tem tanto em suas mãos, então</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Малышка у тебя такая власть надо мной поэтому</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Piccola, hai una tale presa su di me, quindi</span></p>
