      <p begin="03:24.620" end="03:28.680" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L64"><span begin="03:24.620" end="03:24.820">You</span> <span begin="03:24.820" end="03:24.910">mu</span><span begin="03:24.910" end="03:25.010">st</span> <span begin="03:25.010" end="03:25.220">be</span> <span begin="03:25.220" end="03:25.350">an</span> <span begin="03:25.350" end="03:25.680">an</span><span begin="03:25.680" end="03:26.630">gel</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你一定是不慎坠入凡间的天使</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你一定是不慎墜入凡間的天使</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君は天使に違いない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">넌 틀림없이 천사일 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tu dois être un ange</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Debes ser un ángel</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Du musst ein Engel sein</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Você deve ser um anjo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ты должно быть ангел</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Devi essere un angelo</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="03:26.000" end="03:28.680"><span begin="03:26.000" end="03:26.170">(You</span> <span begin="03:26.170" end="03:26.280">mu</span><span begin="03:26.280" end="03:26.370">st</span> <span begin="03:26.370" end="03:26.530">be</span> <span begin="03:26.530" end="03:26.660">an</span> <span begin="03:26.730" end="03:27.060">an</span><span begin="03:27.060" end="03:28.680">gel)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你一定是不慎坠入凡间的天使</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你一定是不慎墜入凡間的天使</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君は天使に違いない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">넌 틀림없이 천사일 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tu dois être un ange</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Debes ser un ángel</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Du musst ein En