      <p begin="03:27.380" end="03:28.680" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L65"><span begin="03:27.380" end="03:27.500">Pu</span><span begin="03:27.500" end="03:27.580">t</span> <span begin="03:27.580" end="03:27.770">you</span> <span begin="03:27.770" end="03:27.900">in</span> <span begin="03:27.900" end="03:28.020">a</span> <span begin="03:28.020" end="03:28.090">f</span><span begin="03:28.090" end="03:28.430">rame,</span> <span begin="03:28.430" end="03:28.680">ooh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">真想把你珍藏进画框里 喔</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">真想把你珍藏進畫框裡 喔</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君を額縁に飾りたい</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">널 액자에 담아두고 싶어, 우</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Te mettre dans un cadre ouh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Te pondría en un marco, oh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich würde dich am liebsten einrahmen oh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Te colocaria numa moldura, ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Поместить бы тебя в рамку оох</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Da metterti in una cornice, oh</span></p>
      <p begin="03:28.740" end="03:30.010" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L66"><span begin="03:28.740" end="03:28.910">Ba</span><span begin="03:28.910" end="03:29.100">by,</span> <span begin="03:29.100" end="03:29.250">who</span> <span begin="03:29.250" end="03:29.310">could</span> <span begin="03:29.420" end="03:29.460">b</span><span begin="03:29.460" end="03:29.780">lame</span> <span begin="03:29.780" end="03:30.010">you?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">宝贝 谁又能舍得怪你呢？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">寶貝 誰又能捨得怪你呢？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">ベイビー 誰が君を責められる</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">베이비, 누가 널 탓하겠어?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Bébé qui pourrait t'en blâmer ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Nena, ¿quién podría culparte?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Schatz wer könnte es dir verübeln</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Baby, quem poderia te culpar?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Малышка кто бы мог тебя винить</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Piccola, chi potrebbe biasimarti?</span></p>
      <p begin="03:30.100" end="03:33.420" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L67"><span begin="03:30.100" end="03:30.280">Gla</span><span begin="03:30.280" end="03:30.320">d</span> <span begin="03:30.320" end="03:30.480">your</span> <span begin="03:30.480" end="03:30.640">ma</span><span begin="03:30.640" end="03:30.820">ma</span> <span begin="03:30.820" end="03:31.130">ma</span><span begin="03:31.130" end="03:31.170">de</span> <span begin="03:31.170" end="03:31.730">you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">万分庆幸你母亲带你降临人世</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">萬分慶幸你母親帶你降臨人世</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君を産んでくれたママに感謝するよ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">널 낳아주신 네 어머니께 감사해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Heureux que ta maman t'ait faite</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Agradezco que tu mamá te haya dado la vida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Bin froh dass deine Mama dich zur Welt gebracht hat</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Que bom que a sua mãe te fez</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я так рад что твоя мама родила тебя</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sono grato che tua madre ti abbia messa al mondo</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="03:31.430" end="03:33.420"><span begin="03:31.430" end="03:31.660">(Gla</span><span begin="03:31.660" end="03:31.700">d</span> <span begin="03:31.700" end="03:31.800">your</span> <span begin="03:31.860" end="03:31.970">ma</span><span begin="03:32.010" end="03:32.130">ma</span> <span begin="03:32.190" end="03:32.490">ma</span><span begin="03:32.490" end="03:32.550">de</span> <span begin="03:32.550" end="03:33.420">you)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">万分庆幸你母亲带你降临人世</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">萬分慶幸你母親帶你降臨人世</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君を産んでくれたママに感謝するよ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">널 낳아주신 네 어머니께 감사해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Heureux que ta maman t'ait faite</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Agradezco que tu mamá te haya dado la vida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Bin froh dass deine Mama dich zur Welt gebracht hat</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Que bom que a sua mãe te fez</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я так рад что твоя мама родила тебя</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sono grato che tua madre ti abbia messa al mondo</span></span></p>
