      <p begin="03:35.530" end="03:37.540" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L70"><span begin="03:35.530" end="03:35.730">You</span> <span begin="03:35.730" end="03:35.820">mu</span><span begin="03:35.820" end="03:35.940">st</span> <span begin="03:35.940" end="03:36.130">be</span> <span begin="03:36.130" end="03:36.260">an</span> <span begin="03:36.260" end="03:36.590">an</span><span begin="03:36.590" end="03:37.540">gel</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你一定是不慎坠入凡间的天使</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你一定是不慎墜入凡間的天使</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君は天使に違いない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">넌 틀림없이 천사일 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tu dois être un ange</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Debes ser un ángel</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Du musst ein Engel sein</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Você deve ser um anjo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ты должно быть ангел</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Devi essere un angelo</span></p>
      <p begin="03:38.290" end="03:41.630" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L71"><span begin="03:38.290" end="03:38.680">Jea</span><span begin="03:38.680" end="03:38.850">lou</span><span begin="03:38.850" end="03:38.990">s,</span> <span begin="03:40.010" end="03:40.200">bu</span><span begin="03:40.200" end="03:40.240">t</span> <span begin="03:40.240" end="03:40.390">I</span> <span begin="03:40.510" end="03:41.000">can't</span> <span begin="03:41.000" end="03:41.420">hel</span><span begin="03:41.420" end="03:41.460">p</span> <span begin="03:41.460" end="03:41.630">it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">为你吃醋嫉妒 但我也情难自禁</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">為你吃醋嫉妒 但我也情難自禁</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">嫉妬してしまうけど 仕方がないんだ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">질투 나지만, 어쩔 수 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Jaloux mais je n'y peux rien</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Celoso, pero no puedo evitarlo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Eifersüchtig aber ich kann nichts dafür</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Com ciúmes, mas não consigo evitar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ревную но ничего не могу с собой поделать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Geloso, ma non ci posso fare niente</span></p>
      <p begin="03:42.890" end="03:47.150" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L72"><span begin="03:42.890" end="03:43.230">I</span> <span begin="03:43.230" end="03:43.750">wan</span><span begin="03:43.750" end="03:43.790">t</span> <span begin="03:43.790" end="03:44.050">e</span><span begin="03:44.050" end="03:44.100">ve</span><span begin="03:44.100" end="03:44.160">ry</span> <span begin="03:44.260" end="03:44.580">bi</span><span begin="03:44.580" end="03:44.620">t</span> <span begin="03:44.620" end="03:44.790">of</span> <span begin="03:44.790" end="03:45.420">you,</span> <span begin="03:45.420" end="03:45.510">I</span> <span begin="03:45.630" end="03:45.800">gue</span><span begin="03:45.800" end="03:45.990">ss</span> <span begin="03:45.990" end="03:46.390">I'm</span> <span begin="03:46.390" end="03:46.790">sel</span><span begin="03:46.790" end="03:46.990">fi</span><span begin="03:46.990" end="03:47.150">sh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我想要霸占你的每一分每一寸 我想我就是这般自私</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我想要霸佔你的每一分每一寸 我想我就是這般自私</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君の全てが欲しい 僕は自分勝手なんだろう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">너의 모든 것을 원해, 내가 이기적인가 봐</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je veux chaque parcelle de toi je suppose que je suis égoïste</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Quiero cada parte de ti, supongo que soy egoísta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich will jedes Stückchen von dir ich glaube ich bin selbstsüchtig</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu quero cada pedacinho seu, acho que sou egoísta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я хочу каждую частичку тебя наверное я эгоист</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Voglio ogni singola parte di te, credo di essere egoista</span></p>
    </div>
